<br>
1) in RvR its often several of them onto you (reduced defence and dificult to time the style)<br>
2) enemy players use styles that give a bonus to hit (reduced chance to evade)<br>
3) If there are many players near by you'll be slightly laged. <br>
4) Many oponants move arround and so you'll only land 2 out of 3 blows (so will they but it screws reactive styles).<br>
4) After the fight begins you rarely have more than 3 blows before you've been shot / nuked / stuned / petted to death.<br>
<br>
The CS style which chains off evade is excelent because it adds to your defence does lots of damage and is low ish stamina - that means that if you have 3 oponants you get improved defence against all of them rather than just a stun against one of them (once).<br>
<br>
Dragonfang would not get a place on my hotbar if it were a L30 thrust style.<br>
<br>
Edit: And your not just giving up Lifebane with envenom buffed to 40 but also the best snare, best enervate and the best disease. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aach</A> at: 4/6/02 5:36:39 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.showPrevMessage?topicID=137.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.showNextMessage?topicID=137.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=137.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.emailToFriend?topicID=137.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.threadControl?topicID=137.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=137.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm22.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=137.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontr